    High-Quality Material  </h3>
<div class="taxonomy-term-description">You’re here because you’re looking for the highest quality material on your new 14-inch Razer Blade 2016 skin. Want to know what the difference is between the material used on ACellShop 2016 14” Razer Blade skins and materials used by other companies? It’s quite simple: only ACellShop uses authentic, true-textured 3M vinyl on every single product we make, including all our 14-inch New Razer Blade skins. When you decide to take off your 14” 2016 Razer Blade skin, there’s no need to fear that it’ll leave any residue on your laptop. It’s not imitation knockoff vinyl… only the highest grade 3M materials on earth. To add to this, there’s a few Razer Blade 14-inch skins that are only available from dbrand, made possible through our massive buying power with 3M. ACellShop 14” Razer Blade skins for the 2016 New Razer Blade: quality materials, simple installation, and the ultimate in precision-fit. Our experience in manufacturing and exclusive use of only the best materials available provides confidence behind our bold claims.</div></div>
