    Our Variety, Your Choice  </h3>
<div class="taxonomy-term-description">Take a second to scroll up and check out our 14” Razer Blade 2016 skin customization interface. Come back down here when you’re done, we’ll wait. What you just experienced was the most innovative, interactive Razer Blade skin customization tool in existence; a unique tool which allows you to get a live preview of exactly what your 14-inch 2016 New Razer Blade skin will look like once it arrives. From Matte Black with no logo to Carbon Fiber with an exposed three-headed Razer serpent, we’ve got a Razer Blade 2016 skin to suit your style. Using our customizer, you can change the look of the top, bottom, trackpad, and even delete the logo to build a look which is entirely custom to your New 2016 Razer Bade 14”.</div></div>
